<style>
  .highlight {
    background-color: yellow;
  }
</style>

<strong>JSON Filter (json) - used to format an object in JSON format</strong>
{{ collection.products.first | json }}
{{ shop | json }}
<strong>Note: JSON Filter may not work on some objects like 'shop' as shown above</strong>
<br/>

<strong>Default Filter (default: default_value) - used to specify a default value</strong>
Description of collection '{{ collection.title }}' - {{ collection.description | default: 'This is a default description' }}
<br/>


<strong>Highlight Filter (Highlight: string) - used to Highlight a substring</strong>
{{ collection.description | highlight: "This is" }}
<br/>
